{
  "clauseRiskSummary": "This clause is a standard 'further assurances' provision, which doesn't raise significant risk for the client. It merely requires the parties to take reasonable actions to facilitate the agreement.",
  "operative_text": "Each Party shall, at its own expense, execute and deliver such other documents and perform such other acts as may be reasonably necessary to effect this Assignment.",
  "concerns": [
    {
